From 3f4d21741f8b0836a3186debd90b6f4ffbdc863f Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: dylanyunlong <dylanyunlong@gmail.com>
Date: Mon, 23 Mar 2026 16:02:46 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat(frontend): add Agentic Loop Event Stream Monitor with 63
 command types

- 63 command types across 14 categories (SSE Protocol, Cognition, Text Output,
  Tool Framework, Shell, File Operations, Search & Process, Git Operations,
  Packages, Containers, Execution, Network, Archive & Patch, Database)
- 56 demo events derived from real eventStream1-4 SSE data
- 3 view modes: Stream (collapsible timeline), Compact (grid), Reference (type catalog)
- Category filtering, text search, expand/collapse all controls
- Real SSE protocol structure: message_start/stop/delta, content_block_start/stop/delta,
  thinking/thinking_delta/thinking_summary, tool_use/tool_result, input_json_delta
- Collapsible panels with syntax-highlighted command output, error states, status badges
- Rate limit utilization bars from message_limit events
- 33 SVG icon set covering all tool categories
- Sticky header with glassmorphism backdrop-filter
- Dark theme with IBM Plex Mono typography

Source data: eventStream1.txt, eventStream2.txt, eventStream3.txt, eventStream4.txt
